-- South African Reserve Bank Won't Make Capital Distribution to Shareholders
-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 2010-12-08T09:00:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/south-african-reserve-bank-won-t-make-capital-distribution-to-shareholders.html
South Africa’s central bank won’t
make a capital distribution to shareholders, Governor Gill
Marcus said at the company’s annual general meeting in Pretoria
today in response to demands from some investors.  “No legal basis exists for a capital distribution,”
Marcus said. “This demand shouldn’t be entertained.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
